Project description

SymEngine is a standalone fast C++ symbolic manipulation library.Optional thin Python wrappers (SymEngine) allow easy usage from Python andintegration with SymPy and Sage.

See https://github.com/symengine/symengine.py for information about Licenseand dependencies of wheels
